Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.02,Default,AKAI,0,0,0,,عُلِم
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.99,Default,HISHINUMA,0,0,0,,مـ.. ما الذي يحدث؟
